These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, mirinda, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, disaster, superhero, spy
There are 5 different nationalities: american, russian, pakistani, australian, canadian
5 different pets are kept: snake, pony, mouse, ferret, goat
 1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the owner of the snake is the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the russian and the person watching spy movies##2
12. the australian is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | fanta        | juice | hot-chocolate     | mirinda   | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | martial-arts      | superhero | spy   | romance    |
| Nationality   | australian  | russian     | american | pakistani | canadian  |
| Pet           | pony | mouse      | goat     | ferret   | snake     |

