.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, traveling, baking, singing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, jazz, trance, indie, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, colombian, italian, thai, egyptian
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, subway, train, tram, boat
 1. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the colombian##1
 5. the person driving the subway is between the russian and the fan of rock##2
 6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the italian is the fan of indie##1
 9. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
11. the italian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | baking | board-games | singing    | magic-tricks  | traveling    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | jazz       | trance      | soul | indie        |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | colombian     | russian    | thai  | italian     |
| Transport     | train    | subway | boat | tram | airplane |

