.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, baking, writing, drawing, card-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, sports, animation, scientific
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, funk, salsa, trance, folk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, weightlifting, ice-hockey, parkour
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of funk##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fan of folk##1
13. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games     | writing   | baking   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | musical | time-travel | animation | sports        |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | funk      | trance       | folk       | rock       |
| Sport         | sailing | parkour  | ice-hockey    | cycling    | weightlifting        |

