.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: grapefruit, eggplant, cranberry, pomegranate, pepper
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, chess, video-games, drawing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, jazz, hip-hop, soul, folk
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, french, thai, argentine, dutch
 1. the french is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the dutch is between the fan of soul and the person eating pomegranate##2
 5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the right of the thai##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of jazz##1
 9. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
10. the fan of soul is the indian##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the indian is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
13. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | pepper  | cranberry     | pomegranate   | eggplant     | grapefruit |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | card-games    | video-games  | drawing | chess   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | ambient    | folk     | hip-hop     | soul    |
| Nationality   | french    | thai | argentine | dutch | indian   |

