.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, 7up
There 5 different types of food: onion, kale, pumpkin, banana, pineapple
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, coach, firefighter, bartender, police-officer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, soccer, snowboarding, golf
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the analyst##1
 2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person eating onion##2
 5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the coach##1
 8. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the analyst##1
11. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
12. the bartender is on the left of the analyst##1
13. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | 7up       | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate      | sprite    |
| Food       | pineapple | banana        | onion       | pumpkin       | kale |
| Job        | police-officer     | coach        | bartender | analyst        | firefighter  |
| Sport      | snowboarding | soccer | ice-hockey      | golf | water-polo  |

