 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is the spanish##1
 8. the german is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
11. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
12. the person drinking milk is on the right of the mexican##1
13. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1

