5 different pets are kept: cat, fish, bird, hedgehog, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, train, tram, bus
 1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the owner of the bird is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the russian##2
 5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 7. the indonesian is on the right of the australian##1
 8. the pakistani is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is the indonesian##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
11. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the australian##1
12. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing   | writing | hiking  | woodworking | drawing |
| Nationality   | australian | indonesian     | russian   | thai     | pakistani      |
| Pet           | cat       | hedgehog        | fish     | bird      | mouse          |
| Transport     | train      | bus        | quad-bike | tram | scooter       |

