 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
12. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | water       | cola    | hot-chocolate | milk  | lemonade        |
| Hobby       | baking | chess | gardening  | filmmaking | skydiving    |
| Sport       | snowboarding        | biathlon   | rugby  | cycling   | swimming |
| Transport   | bike       | snowmobile      | helicopter      | subway | ship  |

