.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, soy-milk, tea, lemonade
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, architect, software-developer, photographer, journalist
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, sports, time-travel, zombie
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, country, techno, r&b, reggae
 1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the photographer is between the person watching sports movies and the software-developer##2
 3. the person drinking tea is the photographer##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the journalist and the fan of country##2
 7. the fan of r&b is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of techno##1
 9. the fan of punk is on the left of the journalist##1
10. the freelancer is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the software-developer is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
