 6. the chinese is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person driving the bike and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is busd-games##2
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's hobby is busd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is busd-games is on the right of the australian##1

