 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is between the argentine and the fan of dubstep##2
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is the fan of gospel##1
 5. the fan of gospel is between the italian and the fan of r&b##2
 6. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dubstep-climbing is the fan of d&b##1
 9. the british is the fan of d&b##1
10. the person who's hobby is dubstep-climbing is on the right of the mexican##1
11. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1

